      "content": "i know, i read about the stomach thing but i'm literally in agony right now and i can't afford to go to the ER or anything. i just need to know if it's actually dangerous if i just do one big dose to get through the night. like would an extra 400 or 800mg really hurt that much if it's just once? i feel like i'm hitting a wall here.",
